cdata.name: Aussie Digital
cdata.desc:
Aussie Digital is an e-commerce platform that provides financial tools allowing users to invest in the cryptocurrency market. Aussie Digital features a trading platform where users are able to perform cryptocurrencies transactions between them, as well as an e-commerce online store with similarities to e-bay.

The AUD token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is the platform native token and it will serve users as a medium for exchange value, staking or purchasing goods and services.
